1
00:00:06,634 --> 00:00:09,236
[RIEZE]
YES, UNDERSTOOD...

2
00:00:09,336 --> 00:00:11,806
LET ME SEE WHAT I
CAN FIND OUT HERE.

3
00:00:11,906 --> 00:00:14,341
I'LL CALL BACK SHORTLY.

4
00:00:14,441 --> 00:00:15,876
[HENRIETTA]
PARDON ME, MISS RIEZE..

5
00:00:15,976 --> 00:00:16,877
(GASP)

6
00:00:16,977 --> 00:00:18,212
UH?

7
00:00:18,312 --> 00:00:20,480
[RIEZE]
I... I'M SORRY IT'S NOTHING.

8
00:00:20,581 --> 00:00:24,652
I... I JUST KNOW THIS IS
A DESPERATE TIME FOR US.

9
00:00:24,752 --> 00:00:28,756
MAYBE, BUT YOU DON'T HAVE TO
HIDE YOUR FEELINGS FROM US.

10
00:00:29,156 --> 00:00:29,790
MPH...

11
00:00:29,890 --> 00:00:31,291
AH...

12
00:00:31,391 --> 00:00:32,527
[HENRIETTA] LOOK, IF YOU
WANNA TALK ABOUT IT,

13
00:00:32,627 --> 00:00:35,262
I DON'T MIND BEING HERE FOR
YOU, OKAY?

14
00:00:35,362 --> 00:00:37,331
MM. (SNIFFLE)

15
00:02:10,991 --> 00:02:12,126
(STREET CHATTER)

16
00:02:12,226 --> 00:02:14,428
[HENRIETTA] MISA'S SCYTHE
WENT OUT OF CONTROL?!

17
00:02:14,529 --> 00:02:17,698
AND WHAT? IT MADE KRUSTY
VANISH INTO THIN AIR?

18
00:02:17,798 --> 00:02:20,868
[RIEZE] NONE OF US CAN GET OUT
TELEPATHIC CALLS TO GO THROUGH.

19
00:02:20,968 --> 00:02:23,971
AND WE STILL HAVE TO DEAL WITH
THIS SERIAL KILLER MENACE.

20
00:02:24,071 --> 00:02:26,641
IF THERE'S ONE THING WE NEED TO
KEEP UNDER CONTROL, IT'S THAT

21
00:02:26,741 --> 00:02:28,876
WE DON'T WANT ANY INFORMATION
ABOUT THIS TO GET OUT.

22
00:02:28,976 --> 00:02:32,212
YES, YOU MIGHT WANNA KEEP THIS
FROM THE ROUND TABLE.

23
00:02:32,312 --> 00:02:33,814
THE TIMING WOULD NOT BE IDEAL.

24
00:02:33,914 --> 00:02:36,651
WE STILL DON'T KNOW WHO
MINAMI'S SPIES ARE.

25
00:02:36,751 --> 00:02:38,418
I'M WONDERING
IF WE SHOULD

26
00:02:38,519 --> 00:02:40,454
INFORM PRINCESS
RAYNESHIA OR NOT.

27
00:02:40,555 --> 00:02:41,689
DEFINITELY.

28
00:02:41,789 --> 00:02:44,291
AND IF I KNOW KRUSTY
LIKE YOU DO, RIEZE,

29
00:02:44,391 --> 00:02:48,462
HE'LL WALTZ RIGHT BACK TO US
AS IF NOTHING HAPPENED AT ALL.

30
00:02:48,563 --> 00:02:50,097
I SUPPOSE HE WOULD.

31
00:02:50,197 --> 00:02:52,132
(PING)
[HENRIETTA] MPH.

32
00:02:52,232 --> 00:02:54,702
[MIKAKAGE, VOICE CHAT]
HENRIETTA, THIS IS HORRIBLE!

33
00:02:54,802 --> 00:02:56,537
WHAT'S GOING ON MIKAKAGE?

34
00:02:56,637 --> 00:02:58,072
[MIKAKAGE]
THERE'S SOMETHING VERY WRONG

35
00:02:58,172 --> 00:02:59,273
WITH THE FLAVOR TEXTS!

36
00:02:59,373 --> 00:03:00,608
MPH....

37
00:03:05,813 --> 00:03:08,983
[RIEZE] THINGS ARE LITERALLY
BECOMING THEIR DESCRIPTIONS?

38
00:03:09,083 --> 00:03:11,318
[MIKAKAGE] YEAH. EVEN THOUGH
IT'S ALWAYS BEEN THERE

39
00:03:11,418 --> 00:03:12,687
JUST TO ADD AMBIANCE
AND INTRIGUE.

40
00:03:12,787 --> 00:03:15,189
BUT NOW, ANYTHING WRITTEN
IN THE FLAVOR TEXT

41
00:03:15,289 --> 00:03:16,857
IS BECOMING TRUE TO LIFE.

42
00:03:16,957 --> 00:03:19,293
WELL, I GUESS THAT MEANS
WE'LL NEED TO PAY MUCH CLOSER

43
00:03:19,393 --> 00:03:22,129
ATTENTION TO ALL THE ITEM
DESCRIPTIONS FROM NOW ON.

44
00:03:22,229 --> 00:03:25,733
IT COULD START CAUSING ALL KINDS
OF TROUBLE FOR US IF WE DON'T.

45
00:03:25,833 --> 00:03:28,402
[RIEZE, THINKING]
THE FLAVOR TEXT, WORDS GIVING

46
00:03:28,503 --> 00:03:30,004
THEIR OBJECTS UNFORESEEN POWER.

47
00:03:30,104 --> 00:03:34,108
MAYBE THAT'S THE REASON MISA'S
WEAPON ATTACKED HER AND KRUSTY.

48
00:03:34,208 --> 00:03:35,576
TO COMPLICATE MATTERS...

49
00:03:35,676 --> 00:03:38,078
[RIEZE] THE KILLER IS IN
POSSESSION OF BYAKUMARU.

50
00:03:38,178 --> 00:03:40,781
WHO KNOWS WHAT WILL HAPPEN IF
THE FLAVOR TEXT OF THAT

51
00:03:40,881 --> 00:03:42,783
SWORD WERE TO COME TO LIFE!
[BOTH] HUH?

52
00:03:42,883 --> 00:03:45,319
THAT SWORD CAN DO AN INCREDIBLE
AMOUNT OF DAMAGE ON IT'S OWN.

53
00:03:45,419 --> 00:03:48,422
NOW IT'S IN THE HANDS OF
SOMEONE IN ROYAL GUARD ARMOR.

54
00:03:48,523 --> 00:03:49,924
IF I REMEMBER CORRECTLY,

55
00:03:50,024 --> 00:03:52,893
YOU GET BYAKUMARU AS
AN ITEM DROP IN A QUEST.

56
00:03:52,993 --> 00:03:54,762
THAT'S RIGHT, IT'S
ONE OF THE RAIDS

57
00:03:54,862 --> 00:03:56,831
THEY RELEASED IN
EXPANSION‐PACK TEN.

58
00:03:56,931 --> 00:03:59,900
YOU HAD TO BEAT THE DEAD
WARRIOR LUGRIUS TO GET IT.

59
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:03,237
[RIEZE] IT WAS HIS SWORD, AND
IT WAS ABSOLUTELY INCREDIBLE.

60
00:04:03,337 --> 00:04:04,939
DEAD WARRIOR LUGRIUS?

61
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:06,774
[HENRIETTA] SO WHAT
DOES THE FLAVOR TEXT

62
00:04:06,874 --> 00:04:07,875
ON LUGRIUS HAVE TO SAY?

63
00:04:07,975 --> 00:04:09,409
[RIEZE] IT TALKS
ABOUT THE LEGEND

64
00:04:09,510 --> 00:04:11,812
OF LUGRIUS AND HOW HE
TURNED INTO A DEMON.

65
00:04:11,912 --> 00:04:15,049
LUGRIUS ORIGINALLY FOUGHT AS
THE HERO OF THE ICY WALLS

66
00:04:15,149 --> 00:04:18,218
ALONG SIDE THE IZUMO KNIGHTS
FOR A HUNDRED YEARS.

67
00:04:18,318 --> 00:04:19,587
IT'S SAID THAT HE FOUGHT

68
00:04:19,687 --> 00:04:21,722
LONG AND HARD TO DEFEND
THE HEALTH AND HAPPINESS

69
00:04:21,822 --> 00:04:25,793
OF THE SUSUKINO PEOPLE ALWAYS
KEEPING THE EVIL GIANTS AT BAY.

70
00:04:25,893 --> 00:04:29,329
HE WAS TRULY THE EZZO
EMPIRE'S CHAMPION.

71
00:04:31,265 --> 00:04:33,501
HOWEVER...

72
00:04:33,601 --> 00:04:35,870
HOWEVER, THE MAID
OF ELM, SUTUYNAW,

73
00:04:35,970 --> 00:04:38,005
SERVED LUGRIUS
A DEADLY POISON

74
00:04:38,105 --> 00:04:40,541
IN AN UNFORESEEN
ACT OF BETRAYAL.

75
00:04:40,641 --> 00:04:42,977
SHORTLY AFTER,
HE BECAME A MONSTER

76
00:04:43,077 --> 00:04:46,480
FILLED WITH BITTERNESS
AND HATRED FOR EVERYONE.

77
00:04:46,581 --> 00:04:49,650
WELL THAT CERTAINLY DOESN'T
PAINT A BRIGHT LIGHT ON THINGS.

78
00:04:49,750 --> 00:04:51,318
DO YOU THINK THE
EVIL SPIRIT IS REAL?

79
00:04:51,418 --> 00:04:54,421
AND THAT HE'S OUT THERE HELPING
THE KILLER IN THE ARMOR?

80
00:04:54,522 --> 00:04:55,890
[RIEZE]
DON'T BE RIDICULOUS!

81
00:04:55,990 --> 00:04:57,525
[MIKAKAGE] HUH?
(HENRIETTA GASPS)

82
00:04:57,625 --> 00:05:00,561
[RIEZE] I'M TERRIBLY
SORRY ABOUT THAT... I ...

83
00:05:00,661 --> 00:05:02,396
I GUESS MAYBE IT COULD BE,

84
00:05:02,496 --> 00:05:05,499
AND THAT COULD POSSIBLY HELP US
DEVISE A PLAN TO DEFEAT LUGRIS.

85
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,934
[BOTH]
OHHH?

86
00:05:07,034 --> 00:05:08,268
(EXHALE)

87
00:05:17,444 --> 00:05:19,113
(GROANING)

88
00:05:19,213 --> 00:05:23,483
[NERURESU, VOICE STRAINING]
GET OUT OF MY HEAD!

89
00:05:23,584 --> 00:05:26,554
DAMN YOU... I WON'T
BE YOUR PUPPET!

90
00:05:26,654 --> 00:05:29,123
I'M A MEMBER OF
THE ROYAL GUAAAARD!

91
00:05:29,223 --> 00:05:31,025
[LUGRIUS, TAKING OVER NERURESU'S
VOICE] RELEASE YOURSELF,

92
00:05:31,125 --> 00:05:34,795
YOU'RE NOT THIS TOWN'S
FILTHY GUARD DOG.

93
00:05:34,895 --> 00:05:38,699
WITH POWER GREATER
THAN THE ADVENTURERS,

94
00:05:38,799 --> 00:05:40,935
YOU SHOULD BE THEIR HERO.

95
00:05:41,035 --> 00:05:44,271
JOIN ME IN MY VENGEANCE
AGAINST THE MAID OF ELM.

96
00:05:44,371 --> 00:05:49,143
AGAINST ALL THE PUTRID HUMAN
REFUSE SWIMMING AROUND YOU!

97
00:05:57,852 --> 00:06:00,521
[AKATSUKI, THINKING]
FLAVOR TEXT IS COMING TO LIFE.

98
00:06:00,621 --> 00:06:02,389
I WONDER, WHAT WOULD'VE HAPPENED

99
00:06:02,489 --> 00:06:06,193
IF I'D BEEN ABLE TO GET
BYAKUMARU BEFORE THE KILLER DID?

100
00:06:07,494 --> 00:06:09,263
I WAS SO JEALOUS OF MINORI

101
00:06:09,363 --> 00:06:12,366
WHO KNOWS WHAT I WOULD'VE DONE
WITH ALL THAT HATE IN ME?

102
00:06:12,466 --> 00:06:15,135
(INHALE, SIGH)

103
00:06:25,412 --> 00:06:27,014
MPH.

104
00:06:29,517 --> 00:06:30,518
(MUNCH)

105
00:06:30,618 --> 00:06:32,019
[NAZNA]
ARE YOU SURE ABOUT THIS?

106
00:06:32,119 --> 00:06:33,988
UH‐HUH?

107
00:06:34,088 --> 00:06:36,957
I THINK IT'D BE BEST IF I
STAYED OUT OF IT FOR NOW.

108
00:06:37,057 --> 00:06:40,027
BESIDES, I'M SURE MASTER
SHIROE'S GUILDMATE

109
00:06:40,127 --> 00:06:41,696
WILL FIND A
SOLUTION SOON ENOUGH.

110
00:06:41,796 --> 00:06:45,232
SO IT REALLY DOES BOIL
DOWN TO ORAL ARTS?

111
00:06:46,233 --> 00:06:47,034
HM...

112
00:06:47,134 --> 00:06:48,402
THANK YOU.

113
00:06:49,169 --> 00:06:52,673
THE ORAL ARTS ARE QUITE SIMPLE.

114
00:06:52,773 --> 00:06:54,108
(SIPS)

115
00:06:55,610 --> 00:06:59,079
AND AS FOR ME, I HAVE THE
POWER OF MY GIRLS BY MY SIDE.

116
00:06:59,179 --> 00:07:00,815
(EXHALE)

117
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,688
[NAZNA] ALL RIGHT,
WE ALL KNOW THE GOAL

118
00:07:07,788 --> 00:07:09,356
FOR OUR NEW
TRAINING SESSIONS.

119
00:07:09,456 --> 00:07:12,960
FIND AND DESTROY THE SERIAL
KILLER TERRORIZING OUR CITY.

120
00:07:13,060 --> 00:07:14,662
IN KEEPING WITH
RIEZE'S STRATEGY,

121
00:07:14,762 --> 00:07:17,331
THE TRAINING SESSIONS WILL HELP
EVERYONE GET TO KNOW EACH OTHER

122
00:07:17,431 --> 00:07:19,466
AS WELL AS INCREASE YOUR
ABILITIES IN BATTLE.

123
00:07:19,567 --> 00:07:23,437
AND THIS ONE HERE, SHE SAYS SHE
WANTS TO LEARN THE ORAL ARTS.

124
00:07:23,538 --> 00:07:24,905
[AKATSUKI] UH...?
[NAZNA] SO I NEED YOU TO SHOW

125
00:07:25,005 --> 00:07:26,941
HER EVERYTHING YOU'VE
PICKED UP SO FAR.

126
00:07:29,143 --> 00:07:33,347
UH... I'M NOT ALL THAT SKILLED,
BUT YOU HAVE MY FULL DEVOTION!

127
00:07:35,149 --> 00:07:37,117
(LAUGHING) YOU MIGHT
WANNA SAVE THAT

128
00:07:37,217 --> 00:07:38,886
FOR THE GUY YOU END UP MARRYING!

129
00:07:38,986 --> 00:07:40,688
(LAUGHTER) [MIKAKAGE] HENRIETTA
WOULD HAVE LOST HER MIND IF

130
00:07:40,788 --> 00:07:42,056
SHE HEARD YOU SAY
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

131
00:07:42,156 --> 00:07:43,423
(GIGGLING)

132
00:07:43,524 --> 00:07:45,993
[CHIKA] YOU'RE NOT THE ONLY
ONE WHO WANTS TO TOUGHEN UP.

133
00:07:46,093 --> 00:07:47,528
UH...

134
00:07:47,628 --> 00:07:48,729
[SANDY]
MPH...

135
00:07:48,829 --> 00:07:50,197
[KYOKO]
LET'S GET STARTED THEN,

136
00:07:50,297 --> 00:07:51,599
AND TAKE 'EM OUT!

137
00:07:51,699 --> 00:07:54,368
(HAPPY MURMURS/CLAPPING)
[AKATSUKI] OH...

138
00:07:54,468 --> 00:07:57,171
AREN'T YOU GLAD YOU DECIDED
TO COME OUT AND JOIN US?

139
00:07:57,271 --> 00:07:58,105
[AKATSUKI] MM‐HM.

140
00:07:58,205 --> 00:08:00,107
[NAZNA] YOU KNOW
THE DRILL, PEOPLE!

141
00:08:00,207 --> 00:08:02,109
[NAZNA] FIRST IS TO
ACCURATELY JUDGE DISTANCES!

142
00:08:02,209 --> 00:08:03,944
[NAZNA] FIND YOUR RANGE!
[SANDY] GET OUTTA THE WAY!

143
00:08:04,044 --> 00:08:05,445
[KOZARU] I'M NOT REALLY SURE
WHAT ELSE I CAN SAY ABOUT IT.

144
00:08:05,546 --> 00:08:08,015
ANYTHING YOU CAN,
EVERYTHING HELPS!

145
00:08:08,115 --> 00:08:09,950
[YUTA] HMMM...
YOU CAN'T JUST GO

146
00:08:10,050 --> 00:08:12,352
AND LEARN AN ORAL ART
BY CLEARING A RAID,

147
00:08:12,452 --> 00:08:13,988
AND IT'S NOT LIKE IT'S
AND ITEM DROP

148
00:08:14,088 --> 00:08:15,590
FROM KILLING AN
ENEMY OR ANYTHING.

149
00:08:15,690 --> 00:08:16,857
HE'S RIGHT YOU KNOW,

150
00:08:16,957 --> 00:08:18,492
I MEAN THEY'RE REALLY
NOT ALL THAT SPECIAL

151
00:08:18,593 --> 00:08:19,760
WHEN YOU THINK ABOUT 'EM.

152
00:08:19,860 --> 00:08:21,662
[KOZARU] EVEN IF I TOLD
YOU HOW I GOT ONE,

153
00:08:21,762 --> 00:08:24,031
YOU WOULDN'T BE ABLE
TO DO THE SAME THING.

154
00:08:24,131 --> 00:08:27,167
AH, EH... FOR EXAMPLE,

155
00:08:27,267 --> 00:08:29,970
OUR GUILD MASTER LEARNED
HOW TO USE "HYPERION EYE."

156
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:31,338
WE CAN ALL LEARN WHAT IT DOES,

157
00:08:31,438 --> 00:08:33,407
BUT NOT NECESSARILY MASTER IT.
[AKATSUKI] MM‐HM.

158
00:08:33,508 --> 00:08:35,843
EVEN IF HE DOESN'T HAVE A
GOOD LOOK AT HIS TARGET,

159
00:08:35,943 --> 00:08:37,912
HE STILL HAS THE ABILITY
TO DETERMINED WHAT

160
00:08:38,012 --> 00:08:39,313
IT'S HIT POINTS AND STATUS ARE.

161
00:08:39,413 --> 00:08:41,849
SO IF YOU WERE ABLE TO
MASTER SOMETHING LIKE THAT,

162
00:08:41,949 --> 00:08:43,483
YOU CAN FIGURE OUT HOW
MANY HIT POINTS THE GUYS

163
00:08:43,584 --> 00:08:45,753
BEHIND YOU HAVE AND FIGURE
OUT IF THEY'RE A THREAT.

164
00:08:45,853 --> 00:08:46,887
IT'S ACTUALLY PRETTY SWEET!

165
00:08:46,987 --> 00:08:48,155
THAT WOULD BE VERY HELPFUL.

166
00:08:48,255 --> 00:08:49,690
[KOZARU]
BUT UNFORTUNATELY,

167
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:51,491
HE'S THE ONLY PERSON WE
KNOW WHO CAN USE IT.

168
00:08:51,592 --> 00:08:52,727
[AKATSUKI] UH...?

169
00:08:52,827 --> 00:08:54,261
THERE IS NO GUARANTEE
YOU CAN MASTER IT.

170
00:08:54,361 --> 00:08:55,863
EVEN IF YOU LEARN
THE FIRST LEVEL.

171
00:08:55,963 --> 00:08:57,264
(EXHALES)

172
00:08:58,332 --> 00:09:00,835
I'LL TAKE WHAT I CAN GET!
PLEASE HELP ME!

173
00:09:00,935 --> 00:09:02,302
(FIGHTING NOISES)
[BOTH] HYAH!

174
00:09:03,871 --> 00:09:05,305
[AKATSUKI]
UH!

175
00:09:05,606 --> 00:09:06,240
UH?!

176
00:09:06,340 --> 00:09:07,007
(GROAN)

177
00:09:07,107 --> 00:09:08,709
[YUTA] MM.
[KOZARU] HWAH.

178
00:09:08,809 --> 00:09:10,144
(STRUGGLING)

179
00:09:11,011 --> 00:09:12,212
[AKATSUKI]
LET'S TRY IT AGAIN!

180
00:09:12,312 --> 00:09:13,447
UH?

181
00:09:14,515 --> 00:09:16,551
MMM... (SIGH)

182
00:09:16,651 --> 00:09:22,389
(LUNCH CHATTER)

183
00:09:24,825 --> 00:09:26,627
[AKATSUKI, THINKING] ORAL ARTS.

184
00:09:26,727 --> 00:09:28,996
PLEASE SHOW ME
SOME SORT OF CLUE.

185
00:09:29,096 --> 00:09:30,565
[MIKAKAGE]
HEY, AKATSUKI!

186
00:09:30,665 --> 00:09:31,465
HUH?

187
00:09:32,833 --> 00:09:34,902
I MADE SOMETHING FOR
YOU... IT'S SPECIAL.

188
00:09:35,002 --> 00:09:36,871
WHAT DO YOU MEAN IT'S SPECIAL?

189
00:09:36,971 --> 00:09:38,338
(BOTH GIGGLE)

190
00:09:39,607 --> 00:09:41,175
[AKATSUKI]
HUH?

191
00:09:43,578 --> 00:09:47,915
OH‐UH, UH... (PLEASANT SIGH)

192
00:09:49,183 --> 00:09:51,686
[HENRIETTA] OUR KILLER IS A
MEMBER OF THE ROYAL GUARD.

193
00:09:51,786 --> 00:09:55,422
HE IS A PERSON OF THE LAND IN
POSSESSION OF MOVABLE ARMOR...

194
00:09:55,523 --> 00:09:58,659
AND HE IS ARMED WITH THE SWORD
OF THE COLD, BYAKUMARU.

195
00:09:58,759 --> 00:10:02,062
IT'S USUAL ATTACK IS BLIZZARD
AND FREEZE AND IT CAN INFLICT

196
00:10:02,162 --> 00:10:04,131
ITS DAMAGE AT GREAT
RANGE ON ITS TARGET.

197
00:10:04,231 --> 00:10:07,067
I REMEMBER HIM. WASN'T
LUGRIUS A RAID BOSS?

198
00:10:07,167 --> 00:10:10,237
YES. AND KNOWING THAT
SHOULD HELP US DEFEAT HIM.

199
00:10:10,337 --> 00:10:12,673
ASSUMING THE FLAVOR TEXT
HOLDS TRUE FOR BOTH,

200
00:10:12,773 --> 00:10:14,374
IT SHOULD ENLIGHTEN
US IN THREE WAYS.

201
00:10:14,474 --> 00:10:16,744
FIRST, THE SWORD
WILL USE BLIZZARD

202
00:10:16,844 --> 00:10:18,646
TO INFLICT THE FREEZE
STATUS EFFECT.

203
00:10:18,746 --> 00:10:21,348
SECOND, IT WILL INCREASE ALL OF
THE STATS OF THE PERSON

204
00:10:21,448 --> 00:10:23,618
WITH THE SWORD, MULTIPLIED
BY HIS OPPOSITION.

205
00:10:23,718 --> 00:10:27,555
EVERY OFFENSIVE AND DEFENSIVE
STATISTIC FOR BYAKUMARU'S MASTER

206
00:10:27,655 --> 00:10:31,726
WILL GO UP FOR EVERY PLAYER THAT
OPPOSES HIM WITHIN FIFTY METERS.

207
00:10:31,826 --> 00:10:33,493
AHHH... (SIGH)

208
00:10:33,594 --> 00:10:37,097
MEANING THAT OVERWHELMING HIM
WITH NUMBERS ISN'T GONNA WORK.

209
00:10:37,197 --> 00:10:40,568
THAT'S WHERE OUR STRATEGY COMES
IN. IT'S STILL POSSIBLE TO USE

210
00:10:40,668 --> 00:10:43,403
A RAID PARTY IN THIS SITUATION,
BUT WITH A DIFFERENT TACTIC.

211
00:10:43,504 --> 00:10:47,074
WE STILL USE OUR TWENTY‐FOUR,
WITH THE USUAL SIX SPLIT IN TWO

212
00:10:47,174 --> 00:10:50,110
OR THREE, BUT SCATTERED ACROSS
THE CITY LIKE A NET.

213
00:10:50,210 --> 00:10:52,513
YOU WANT TO HOLD A FULL
RAID INSIDE THE CITY.

214
00:10:52,613 --> 00:10:55,149
[RAYNESHIA, THINKING]
PRETTY AMAZING, RIEZE.

215
00:10:55,249 --> 00:10:57,518
YOU CAN TELL SHE'S IN CHARGE OF
THE DEVELOPMENT AND TRAINING

