OUT A LITTLE BIT?

295
00:14:35,670 --> 00:14:38,105
[AKATSUKI] THANKS FOR ASKING,
CHIEF, BUT I'M ALL RIGHT.

296
00:14:38,205 --> 00:14:40,608
YOU SURE ABOUT THAT?

297
00:14:40,708 --> 00:14:42,409
