I'M NOT STRONG ENOUGH.

312
00:15:24,919 --> 00:15:27,354
[NAZNA] COME ON YOU GUYS! KEEP
YOUR DISTANCE.

313
00:15:27,454 --> 00:15:29,557
NOW! SLIP IN BEHIND YOUR ENEMY!

314
00:15:29,657 --> 00:15:31,225
YOU NEED TO BE IN
A CONSTANT STATE

315
00:15:31,325 --> 00:15:32,927
