316
00:15:33,027 --> 00:15:35,763
KNOW WHAT YOU CAN DO AND BE
AWARE OF WHAT YOU CANNOT DO,

317
00:15:35,863 --> 00:15:38,533
SO IT DOESN'T TAKE YOU BY
SURPRISE IN THE FIGHT.

318
00:15:38,633 --> 00:15:40,234
MM.

319
00:15:41,502 --> 00:15:44,271
[AKATSUKI, THINKING]
I KNOW THAT I'M WEAK...

320
00:15:44,371 --> 00:15:46,440
BUT THERE ARE SOME THINGS
I CAN ONLY LEARN

321
