MY WEAKNESSES ARE.

322
00:15:48,208 --> 00:15:49,544
(SCREAM)

323
00:15:49,644 --> 00:15:51,546
[AKATSUKI, THINKING]
I'VE LEARNED FROM DEFEAT,

324
00:15:51,646 --> 00:15:53,648
AND FOUND A PURPOSE
IN MY LACK OF TALENT.

325
00:15:53,748 --> 00:15:55,015
(STRUGGLING)

326
00:15:55,115 --> 00:15:56,383
[AKATSUKI, THINKING]
BUT STILL,

327
00:15:56,483 --> 00:15:58,819
I CAN'T DO EVERYTHING MY OWN...

328
