334
00:16:13,734 --> 00:16:15,836
[AKATSUKI] UH... THANK YOU!
[KAWARA] EHEE!

335
00:16:15,936 --> 00:16:17,404
[AKATSUKI, THINKING] I CAN LEARN
TEAMWORK

336
00:16:17,505 --> 00:16:20,107
AND GET STRONG AT THE SAME TIME!

337
00:16:20,207 --> 00:16:22,476
[NAZNA] Y'KNOW,
YOU SURE ARE TINY.

338
00:16:22,577 --> 00:16:24,779
LEARN TO USE IT
TO YOUR ADVANTAGE.

339
00:16:24,879 --> 00:16:25,980
[AKATSUKI] HUH?

340
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:27,748
THINK ABOUT HOW BIG HE IS.

341
00:16:27,848 --> 00:16:29,349
IT'LL DRIVE HIM NUTS IF YOU
KEEP MOVING AROUND

342
00:16:29,449 --> 00:16:31,151
AND HE CAN'T HIT YOU.

343
00:16:31,251 --> 00:16:34,188
HE SHOULD HAVE A
TON OF BLIND SPOTS.

344
00:16:34,288 --> 00:16:36,791
COME ON, THEN. GIVE IT A TRY.

345
00:16:36,891 --> 00:16:38,258
(GROWL)

346
00:16:38,358 --> 00:16:39,159
(GRUNT)

347
00:16:39,259 --> 00:16:41,361
[RICHO] HUH? (GRUNTS)

348
00:16:41,461 --> 00:16:42,897
[AKATSUKI, THINKING] UNTIL NOW,
I THOUGHT BEING SMALL

349
00:16:42,997 --> 00:16:44,198
WAS ALWAYS WORKING AGAINST ME.

350
00:16:44,298 --> 00:16:45,900
[RICHO] HWAH!
[AKATSUKI, THINKING] BUT I CAN

