I STILL NEED TO BE MINDFUL

353
00:16:49,737 --> 00:16:51,405
OF WHAT I CAN AND
CANNOT DO, THOUGH

354
00:16:51,506 --> 00:16:52,907
(RUNNING, SEINE
STRUGGLING BEHIND)

