THAT SUPPOSED TO MEAN?!

430
00:20:28,088 --> 00:20:29,256
UH...

431
00:20:30,457 --> 00:20:32,527
IF I HAD KNOWN...

432
00:20:38,198 --> 00:20:40,835
I NEVER WOULD HAVE
SOLD IT TO HIM.

433
00:20:40,935 --> 00:20:44,071
[RIEZE] THERE'S NO WAY
YOU COULD KNOW. IT'S FINE.

434
00:20:49,577 --> 00:20:52,547
[RAYNESHIA, THINKING] I WILL NOT
RUN FROM THIS RESPONSIBILITY...

435
00:20:52,647 --> 00:20:53,981
IF I DO THINGS
THE WAY I USED TO,

436
00:20:54,081 --> 00:20:56,283
LETTING OTHER PEOPLE
FIGHT MY BATTLES FOR ME,

437
00:20:56,383 --> 00:20:57,818
I'LL BE SHOWING EVERYONE THAT

438
00:20:57,918 --> 00:21:00,555
I CAN NEVER BE TRUSTED WITH
THE WORK THAT BEFITS MY TITLE.

439
00:21:00,655 --> 00:21:03,023
AND I COULD NEVER BE
WORTHY OF THEIR FRIENDSHIP!

440
00:21:03,123 --> 00:21:04,458
(KNOCKING)

441
00:21:04,559 --> 00:21:05,593
(DOOR OPENING)
[HENRIETTA] UH...

442
00:21:05,693 --> 00:21:07,762
PRINCESS RAYNESHIA!

443
00:21:07,862 --> 00:21:10,164
I NEED TO HAVE A
PART IN THIS QUEST!

444
00:21:10,264 --> 00:21:13,968
PERHAPS AS THE TWENTY SIXTH
MEMBER OF THE SUIFUU MAIDENS,

445
00:21:14,068 --> 00:21:15,302
WILL THAT DO?

446
00:21:27,948 --> 00:21:29,116
[AKATSUKI, THINKING] IN THE END,

447
00:21:29,216 --> 00:21:31,986
I HAVE FAILED TO MASTER
A SINGLE ORAL ART.

448
00:21:32,787 --> 00:21:34,354
BUT THAT'S OKAY...

449
00:21:35,322 --> 00:21:37,658
I NOW HAVE A TEAM I TRUST!

450
00:21:41,095 --> 00:21:43,230
TAKE CARE OF
YOURSELVES OUT THAT.

451
00:21:43,330 --> 00:21:44,932
NOW GIVE IT ALL YOU GOT!

452
00:21:45,032 --> 00:21:47,067
[ALL] YEAH!
[DOLCHE] YOU GO GIRL!

453
00:21:49,537 --> 00:21:51,238
NEW YEAR'S EVE IS HERE.

454
00:21:51,338 --> 00:21:53,073
MM.

455
00:21:53,173 --> 00:21:55,676
TIME TO GIVE HIM
THE END HE DESERVES.

456
00:22:06,220 --> 00:22:07,287
(SURPRISED GASP)

457
00:22:09,557 --> 00:22:11,892
[NERURESU]
YOU'RE KIDDING ME...

458
00:22:11,992 --> 00:22:13,193
(INHALE)

459
00:22:13,293 --> 00:22:18,198
YOU'RE NOT TAKING ME VERY
SERIOUSLY... JUST TWO OF YOU?

460
00:22:18,298 --> 00:22:21,569
WELL, TIME TO DIE...
(GASP)

461
00:22:21,669 --> 00:22:24,004
YOU'LL BE BOWING ON
YOUR HANDS AND KNEES

462
00:22:24,104 --> 00:22:29,810
LIKE ALL THE OTHER COMMONERS...
BEFORE I TAKE THEIR LIVES.

463
00:22:29,910 --> 00:22:35,249
JUST LIKE THE MAID OF ELM, YOU
WILL PAY FOR YOUR BETRAYAL!

464
00:22:35,349 --> 00:22:37,017
YOU DON'T DESERVE TO LIVE!

465
00:22:37,117 --> 00:22:38,252
LET'S GO!

466
00:22:38,352 --> 00:22:39,253
HMPH!

467
00:24:15,382 --> 00:24:17,051
[AKATSUKI, VOICEOVER]
THE RAID IS UNDERWAY!

468
00:24:17,151 --> 00:24:19,920
THE MURDERER'S SWORD SHINES
WITH THE POWER OF A BLIZZARD.

469
00:24:20,020 --> 00:24:23,190
THE CONVICTION OF TWENTY‐SIX
COMRADES DRIVES THE FIGHT.

470
00:24:23,290 --> 00:24:25,693
BUT FATE CAN BE A
FLICKERING FLAME.

471
00:24:25,793 --> 00:24:27,795
JUST AS THE CITY
SINKS INTO DESPAIR,

472
00:24:27,895 --> 00:24:30,665
A TWENTY‐SEVENTH MAIDEN
APPEARS WITH A MIGHTY WEAPON!

473
00:24:30,765 --> 00:24:33,768
AND A PROFOUND SECRET
IS FINALLY DISCOVERED.

474
00:24:34,669 --> 00:24:37,004
[SHIROE]
STAND UP, ONE MORE TIME!

